{"title":"Orto Eleccion de prótesis-2026","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría/Orto Eleccion de prótesis-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Elección de Tipos de Prótesis\\Nen Fractura de Cadera","guid":"8tpx5GCuU0GME62VQEtFSA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Contexto Clínico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Fractura de cadera →\\Ncomplicación grave de\\Nosteoporosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Mortalidad **24% al año**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Solo **50%** recupera\\Nfuncionalidad previa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Objetivo quirúrgico → devolver\\Nfuncionalidad + control dolor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Tratamiento conservador → inmovilidad,\\Ndeformidad, deterioro funcional grave","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"**Elección basada en estado funcional\\Nprevio** > edad cronológica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación Anatómica","guid":"mJ363oaABUqnah7-ixdfTA","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Fracturas Intracapsulares (Mediales)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Localización → cuello femoral\\N(subcapital, transcervical)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Vascularización → **comprometida**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"Complicación principal → **necrosis\\Navascular (NAV)** / pseudoartrosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"Manejo → artroplastia (HA o ATC)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"8","text":"Fracturas Extracapsulares (Laterales)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Localización →\\Nintertrocantérea,\\Nsubtrocantérea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Vascularización → **no\\Ncomprometida**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"Complicación principal →\\N**hemorragia severa** (hasta **3L**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"Manejo →\\Nosteosíntesis (clavos o\\NDHS)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"0","text":"Evidencia: Estudio HEALTH","guid":"ymXZN5V5NEuqNvGxkw0y3w","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Diseño → RCT multicéntrico,\\N**n=1495**, ≥50 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"Inclusión → fractura cuello\\Nfemoral desplazada +\\Ndeambulación independiente\\Nprevia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"Comparación → ATC vs HA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"19","text":"Outcome primario → procedimiento\\Nsecundario a **24 meses**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"19","text":"Resultados principales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Procedimientos secundarios → ATC\\N**7.9%** vs HA **8.3%** (HR 0.95,\\NIC95% 0.64-1.40, **p=0.79**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Análisis post-hoc → riesgo mayor ATC primer\\Naño, mayor HA después del año (HR 0.23,\\NIC95% 0.08-0.69, **p=0.01**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Mortalidad 24m → ATC **14.3%** vs HA **13.\\N1%** (**p=0.48**) → sin diferencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"24","text":"Luxación → ATC **4.7%** vs HA **2.\\N4%** (HR 2.00, IC99% 0.97-4.09)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"WOMAC → ATC mejoría modesta pero\\N**clínicamente insignificante**","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"Artroplastia Total de Cadera (ATC)","guid":"Bo5CgHKwKUmyI_qt1H8T7w","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Paciente <75 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"**Funcional y activo**\\N(deambulación independiente)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"Alta demanda funcional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Expectativa de vida larga","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"Sin deterioro cognitivo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"30","text":"Características quirúrgicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Tiempo operatorio → media\\N**102 min** (rango 70-151)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Pérdida sanguínea\\N>500cc → **26%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Estadía hospitalaria →\\Nmedia **12.3 días**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"30","text":"Ventajas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"**Mejor función** y calidad\\Nde vida a largo plazo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Menor desgaste acetabular\\N(se reemplaza cotilo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Menor riesgo revisión a 4 años","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"30","text":"Desventajas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"**Mayor riesgo luxación** (RR 2.02)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"Mayor tiempo quirúrgico y sangrado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"30","text":"ATC Doble Movilidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Indicación → alto riesgo luxación\\N(Parkinson, ACV, demencia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"Riesgo luxación similar a ATC\\Nconvencional + abordaje anterolateral","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"Hemiartroplastia (HA)","guid":"tt8EKy3cBkmVBBv5kQLRiA","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Paciente **>75 años**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"**Dependiente / inactivo**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"Expectativa de vida limitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"Movilidad reducida basal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"51","text":"Características quirúrgicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Tiempo operatorio → media\\N**78 min** (rango 43-131)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Pérdida sanguínea >500cc → **7%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Estadía hospitalaria →\\Nmedia **11.5 días**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"51","text":"Ventajas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"**Menor riesgo luxación**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Menor tiempo quirúrgico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"Menor sangrado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"51","text":"Desventajas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"**Peor función** a largo plazo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"**Gran desgaste\\Nacetabular** (cotiloiditis)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"Mayor riesgo revisión >1 año","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"51","text":"HA Unipolar vs Bipolar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Sin diferencias en → mortalidad, reoperación,\\Ntiempo operatorio, pérdida sangre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"Desgaste acetabular → unipolar **20%** vs\\Nbipolar **5%** (a 4 años, NS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"Conversión a ATC →\\Nbipolar **más sencilla**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"Costo → bipolar\\N**2-5x más costosa**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"69","text":"**Unipolar preferible** en la mayoría →\\Nmenor costo, resultados similares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"69","text":"Bipolar reservar → alto riesgo luxación\\N(Parkinson, espasticidad)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"Cementado vs No Cementado","guid":"O3u1w1vP5EybcowGKM4Jig","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"HA cementada (vástago cementado)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"**↓ riesgo mortalidad 12 meses**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"**↓ fracturas periprotésicas**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"Riesgos del cemento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"**↑ embolia pulmonar\\Nintraoperatoria**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"**↑ muerte intraoperatoria**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"Síndrome implantación cemento óseo\\N(SICO) → hipoxia, hipotensión, PCR","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Abordaje Quirúrgico","guid":"CaHTp7tIyEaUXVlkRYgwTA","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Posterior","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Luxación HA/ATC\\Nconvencional →\\N**12-14%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"HA bipolar → **8x mayor**\\Nriesgo luxación vs lateral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"Anterolateral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Luxación → **2%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"**Preferible** para minimizar luxación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"84","text":"ATC doble movilidad + posterior\\N→ riesgo similar a ATC\\Nconvencional + anterolateral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"Fracturas Extracapsulares (Laterales)","guid":"_Rjk_SVKwEKuaYCPFS0WzA","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Tratamiento → reducción\\N+ **osteosíntesis**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"Fracturas estables → **DHS\\N(tornillo deslizante)**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"Fracturas\\Ninestables/conminutas/subtrocantéreas\\N→ **clavo cefalomedular largo**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"Inestables con conminución pared\\Nlateral o trazo invertido (AO A2.2, A2.3,\\NA3) → clavo intramedular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"92","text":"NAV → **infrecuente**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"92","text":"Complicación principal →\\Nhemorragia severa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento\\NConservador\\N(Excepcional)","guid":"cvsvsrGXdEaEJwRex280vQ","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Riesgo quirúrgico\\Ninasumible (ASA IV-V)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"Expectativa vida muy\\Nlimitada (<6 meses a 1 año)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"Demencia avanzada (GDS\\N7) / postración basal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"Fractura intracapsular no desplazada en\\Ninmovilizado + dolor controlado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"100","text":"Rechazo del paciente/familia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"99","text":"Objetivo → **confort y\\Ncuidados paliativos**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"0","text":"Artroplastia de\\NResección\\N(Girdlestone)","guid":"rtnoaxTAXEWDjUTSmbQSXg","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"No deambuladores por otras causas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Deterioro cognitivo severo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"Imposibilidad de reimplantación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"Control infecciones post-artroplastia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"Cirugía de salvataje","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"107","text":"**Resultado funcional catastrófico**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"107","text":"Riesgo incapacidad de caminar\\N→ **45%** en geriátricos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"Algoritmo de Decisión","guid":"6ML502nsEUSk-jqL9odA1g","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"<60 años + fractura medial →\\N**osteosíntesis** (bajo riesgo NAV)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"Garden I-II (no desplazada) →\\Nosteosíntesis con tornillos canulados\\No artroplastia (en mayores)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"Garden III-IV (desplazada)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Joven/activo/buena\\Nfunción → **ATC**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":">75\\Naños/dependiente/inactivo\\N→ **HA parcial**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"Alto riesgo luxación → **ATC doble\\Nmovilidad** o **HA bipolar**","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"0","text":"Datos Medicare (n=61,\\N695) - Edelstein 2023","guid":"jzh-aTIVd0usxFC7ct2_Tg","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"16.6% recibió ATC vs 83.4% HA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"Luxación 12 meses → ATC **2.9%** vs\\NHA **1.9%** (**p=0.001**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"Revisión/conversión 12 meses →\\N**sin diferencia significativa**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"123","text":"Tasa global luxación →\\N**baja en ambos grupos**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento 5 años\\N(Luo 2023, n=139)","guid":"cbJ6qoD6HUuECTsW0rWXVA","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"Sobrevida → ATC 60%\\Nvs HA 54.8% (NS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Harris Hip Score → ATC **81.3** vs\\NHA **73.1** (**p<0.001**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"Erosión acetabular → ATC **0%** vs\\NHA **26.5%** (**p=0.002**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"EQ-5D → ATC **0.69** vs HA\\N**0.63** (**p=0.001**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"128","text":"Luxación → ATC 6.1% vs HA 0% (NS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"128","text":"**THA preferible en activos >75\\Naños** con expectativa >5 años","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"ai4Y-yYI_UK5ypDgXC-njQ","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"Decisión → **VGI + decisión\\Ncompartida**, no solo edad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"ATC cementada → preferir en\\Nfuncionales (↓ fracturas periprotésicas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"HA unipolar → costo-efectiva en\\Ndependientes/expectativa limitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"135","text":"Luxación ATC → evitar flexión >90°, cruzar\\Npiernas, rotaciones extremas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"135","text":"Post-ATC → Terapia Ocupacional para\\Neducación y ayudas técnicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"135","text":"SICO → vigilar\\Nhipoxia/hipotensión durante\\Ncementación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"135","text":"Dolor ingle/muslo + bifosfonatos →\\Ndescartar fractura atípica femoral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"135","text":"HA bipolar → reservar para alto riesgo\\Nluxación, no usar rutinariamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"135","text":"Abordaje anterolateral → preferir\\Npara minimizar luxación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"135","text":"ATC doble movilidad → alternativa\\Ncuando riesgo luxación alto pero\\Nfunción preservada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"135","text":"Girdlestone → resultado\\Ncatastrófico, solo salvataje","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"QuU04_qkoU6Xr8B3wNieXw","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"1. Bhandari M, et al. Total Hip Arthroplasty or\\NHemiarthroplasty for Hip Fracture (HEALTH). N\\NEngl J Med. 2019;381(23):2199-208.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"2. Judge A, et al. Total hip arthroplasty versus\\Nhemiarthroplasty for intracapsular hip fracture. Bone\\NJoint J. 2020;102-B(6):658-60. DOI: 10.\\N1302/0301-620X.102B6.BJJ-2020-0101.R1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"3. Edelstein AI, et al. Hemiarthroplasty Versus Total Hip\\NArthroplasty for Femoral Neck Fracture in Elderly\\NPatients. J Bone Joint Surg Am. 2023;105(21):1695-702.\\NDOI: 10.2106/JBJS.23.00247","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"147","text":"4. Luo S, et al. Total hip arthroplasty versus hemiarthroplasty in the\\Ntreatment of active elderly patients over 75 years with displaced\\Nfemoral neck fractures. BMC Musculoskelet Disord. 2023;24(1):745.\\NDOI: 10.1186/s12891-023-06860-6","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"147","text":"5. NICE Guideline [NG111]. Hip fracture:\\Nmanagement. 2017 (updated 2023).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":152,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto Eleccion de prótesis-2026","id":"map_1529","resolved_references":[]}